components.sequence

Interface Sequence<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, SequenceKernel<T>, Standard<Sequence<T>>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Sequence1L, SequenceDL, SequenceSecondary

    public interface Sequence<T>
extends SequenceKernel<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>
    Additional functionality upon the bare-bones functionality afforded by the SequenceKernel interface. All method implementations must, by design, use only the SequenceKernel methods to perform operations on the component.
    Author:
    Matthew Shoemaker
